import axios from "axios"; import React, { useState } from "react"; function FormularioCadastro() { const [nome, setNome] = useState(""); const [estacao, setEstacao] = useState(""); const [periodo, setPeriodo] = useState(""); const [data, setData] = useState(""); const dados = { nome: nome, estacao: estacao, periodo: periodo, data: data } function submitForm(e) { e.preventDefault(); axios.post("http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservas/", dados) } return (
setNome(e.nome)} className="border border-gray-300 rounded-md py-2 px-4 w-full focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:border-blue-300" />
setData(e.Data)} className="border border-gray-300 rounded-md py-2 px-4 w-full focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:border-blue-300" />
); }; export default FormularioCadastro;
